creator: Elliott O'Donnell
description:
LibriVox recording of Dog Ghosts by Elliott O'Donnell.
Read in English by David Wales
Stories in which ghosts of dogs figure. This is chapter 2, Apparitions Of Dogs, of the book Animal Ghosts Or, Animal Hauntings and the Hereafter. - Summary by david wales
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;dogs; ghosts; apparitions
title: Dog Ghosts
